TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT * FROM (SELECT OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PERIOD_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_POSITIONSEQ, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_POSITION_NAME, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENT_AMOUNT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_EARNING_GROUP, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_UPDATE, CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE2, NVL(CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE3, CS_PARTICIPANT.LASTNAME) GENERICATTRIBUTE3, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE4, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE5, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE6, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE7, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE8, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE9, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE10, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE11, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE12, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE13, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE14, CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICBOOLEAN2, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_TXN_DESCRIPTION, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD, replace(replace(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.txt_Remarks,'MMM',TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'MON')),'YYYY',TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY')) FROM OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL, CS_PARTICIPANT, IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLEDATE, IN_ETL_CONTROL IN_CYCLETYPE WHERE OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.Txt_Settlment_Way='TT' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY=OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_EARNING_GROUP AND NVL(CS_PARTICIPANT.GENERICATTRIBUTE5,'9999') ='BANK' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PROCESSING_UNIT = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT in ($$STR_BUSINESS_UNIT) AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL' AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_STRING = '$$STR_PAYMENT_CYCLE_TYPE' AND IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_FILE_NAME = '$$STR_PROCESSING_UNIT' AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE = IN_CYCLETYPE.TXT_KEY_VALUE AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE = TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ NOT IN (SELECT DEC_PAYMENTDETAILSEQ FROM OUT_PAYMENT_RESULT_TRACE WHERE TXT_STATUS = 'ACTIVE') AND CS_PARTICIPANT.PAYEESEQ = OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DEC_PAYEESEQ AND CS_PARTICIPANT.REMOVEDATE > SYSDATE AND CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE <= TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND CS_PARTICIPANT.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > TO_DATE(IN_CYCLEDATE.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD')) PAYMENT_PARTICIPANT_T ----SGPIWH BU CURRENCY DYNAMIC FILTER WHERE CASE WHEN PAYMENT_PARTICIPANT_T.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT = 'SGPIWH' THEN 1 ELSE CASE WHEN PAYMENT_PARTICIPANT_T.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY <> '$$STR_SGD' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END END = 1
